<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Employee Home Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, red, blue);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .card h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .card p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .card a {
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 3px;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Employee Portal!</h1>
        <p>Access important resources and information related to your employment.</p>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Company News</h2>
            <p>Stay updated with the latest news and announcements from the company.</p>
            <a href="#">Read More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Employee Benefits</h2>
            <p>Explore the comprehensive range of benefits available to employees.</p>
            <a href="#">Learn More</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Training & Development</h2>
            <p>Discover learning opportunities and resources to enhance your skills.</p>
            <a href="#">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>